document.description: This is a example of post created by the admin

body.raw:
# Text Styles in Markdown

This is a regular paragraph of text.

## Headers

# Header 1

## Header 2

### Header 3

## Text Styles

**Bold Text**  
_Italicized Text_  
~~Strikethrough Text~~  
**_Bold and Italicized Text_**

## Lists

### Ordered List

1. Item 1
2. Item 2
3. Item 3

### Unordered List

- Item A
- Item B
  - Subitem B.1
  - Subitem B.2

## Links

[Link Text](https://www.example.com)

## Images

![Alt Text](/portfolio-logo.png)

## Blockquotes

> This is a blockquote.

## Code

`Inline Code`

```python
# Python Code Block
def greet():
    print("Hello, world!")



```
